{{Documentation subpage}} <!-- EDIT TEMPLATE DOCUMENTATION BELOW THIS LINE --> {{Tfm|Update|Update section}}{{Twinkle standard installation}}
==Usage== This template can be used to mark articles or sections with old or out-of-date information.
To add the date when the tag was added, use: : {{Tlx|Update|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}} To specify what parts of the article need updating, use the first unnamed parameter: : {{Tlx|Update|<nowiki>Foo [[bar]] qux</nowiki>}} To display the date of the last update, use the second unnamed parameter: : {{Tlx|Update|{{!}}{{#time:j F Y|-1 month}}}} To mark a section, use: : {{Tlx|Update|type{{=}}section}} or alternatively, use the {{Tl|Update section}} template, which produces a warning that the section (rather than the article) is out of date.
==Example== {{Tlx|Update|documentation}} {{Update|documentation}}
The template detects which [[Wikipedia:Namespace|namespace]] it is used in and changes accordingly: {| class="wikitable" ! Article | {{Update|type=article|demospace=main|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}} |- ! Category | {{Update|type=category|demospace=category|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}} |- ! Template | {{Update|type=template|demospace=template|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}} |}
This template will add articles to [[:Category:Wikipedia articles in need of updating]].
==Alternatives== * If there is a dispute about the need for an update, an out-of-date article or section can be marked with {{Tl|Out of date}}. * {{Tl|Update after}} is an alternative for individual statements that will be out-of-date at a specifiable future date. It is a more recent and preferred alternative to [[Wikipedia:As of]]. It also adds articles to [[:Category:Wikipedia articles in need of updating]]. * See [[Wikipedia:Template_messages/Cleanup#Time-sensitive]] for alternatives unrelated to out-of-date information.
==See also== * {{Tl|Update inline}} - inline version * {{Tl|Recentism}} * {{Tl|Current}} * {{Tl|Time-context}} * {{Tl|When}} * {{Tl|Updated}} * {{Tl|As of}} * {{Tl|Show by date}} * {{Tl|Out of date}} * {{Tl|Update section}}
