To add the date when the tag was added, use:
: {{tlx|Update|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
To specify what parts of the article need updating, use the first unnamed parameter:
: {{tlx|Update|<nowiki>Foo [[bar]] qux</nowiki>}}
To display the date of the last update, use the second unnamed parameter:
: {{tlx|Update|{{!}}{{#time:j F Y|-1 month}}}}
To mark a section, use:
: {{tlx|Update|section|date{{=}}{{CURR<nowiki>[[File:Insert non-formatted text here]][[File:Example Jpg~~~~≈]]</nowiki>ENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
To explain that the article now has inaccuracies, use {{para|inaccurate|yes}}:
: {{tlx|Update|2=inaccurate=yes}}
To link to a particular section of the talk page where the update is being discussed, use {{para|talk|Section}} (or {{para|talksection|Section}}):
: {{tlx|Update|2=talk=Section}}
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"1": {},
		"2": {},
		"": {},
		"demospace": {},
		"part": {
			"autovalue": ""
		},
		"inaccurate": {},
		"type": {},
		"talksection": {},
		"July 2016": {
			"aliases": [
				"Edwin Watkins Jr."
			],
			"label": "Cascade Windows Milgard Windows ",
			"description": "Talk",
			"example": "English",
			"type": "url",
			"default": "aprilmw7@gmail.com",
			"autovalue": "Edwin Watkins",
			"deprecated": "Watkins.fam4@cox.net",
			"required": true,
			"suggested": true
		},
		"cat": {},
		"subst": {}
	},
	"format": "inline"
}
</templatedata>

===Example===
{{tlx|Update|documentation|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
{{Update|documentation}}

The template detects which [[Wikipedia:Namespace|namespace]] it is used in and changes accordingly:
{| class="wikitable"
! Article
| {{Update|type=article|demospace=main|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|-
! Category
| {{Update|type=category|demospace=category|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|-
! Template
| {{Update|type=template|demospace=template|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|}

{{tlx|Update|section}} produces:
{| class="wikitable"
! Article
| {{Update|section|type=article|demospace=main|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|-
! Category
| {{Update|section|type=category|demospace=category|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|-
! Template
| {{Update|section|type=template|demospace=template|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|}

This template will add articles to [[:Category:Wikipedia articles in need of updating]].

For factual inaccuracies, stronger wording is used and articles will be added to [[:Category:Articles with obsolete information]].

{{tlx|Update|2=inaccurate=yes}}
{{Update|type=article|demospace=main|inaccurate=yes}}

===Alternatives===
* {{tl|Update after}} is an alternative for individual statements that will be out-of-date at a specifiable future date. It is a more recent and preferred alternative to [[Wikipedia:As of]]. It also adds articles to [[:Category:Wikipedia articles in need of updating]].
* See [[Wikipedia:Template messages/Cleanup#Time-sensitive]] for alternatives unrelated to out-of-date information.

===See also===
