===Usage===
This template can be used to mark articles or sections with old or out-of-date information.

;To specify what parts of the page need updating, use the first unnamed parameter (or name it {{para|part}} or number it {{para|1}}){{colon}}
: {{tnull|Update|'''part{{=}}the later-life and death material and the <nowiki>[[#Legacy|Legacy]]</nowiki> section'''|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
;To use the template in one specific section, and change its wording to refer to the section instead of the page, use {{para||section}} (this is a special case of {{para|1}} a.k.a. {{para|part}}, above). Insert the template at the top of the page{{colon}}
: {{tnull|Update|'''section'''|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
;To display the date (in whatever format) of the last significant update to the page, use the second unnamed parameter (or name it {{para|updated}} or number it {{para|2}}){{colon}}
: {{tnull|Update|'''updated{{=}}{{#time:j F Y|-1 month}}'''|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
: '''Note:''' The parameter name or number must be used if the first numbered/unnamed parameter is not used.
;To add the date when the tag was added (this is used for cleanup categorization), use{{colon}}
: {{tnull|Update|'''date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}'''}}
: You can also do: <code><nowiki>{{Update|{{subst:DATE}}}}</nowiki></code>
;To explain that the article now has inaccuracies (not just missing information) due to being outdated, use {{para|inaccurate|yes}}{{colon}}
: {{tnull|Update|'''inaccurate{{=}}yes'''|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
;To link to a particular section of the talk page where the update is being discussed, use {{para|talk|{{var|Section title}}}} ({{para|talksection}} and {{para|discuss}} are equivalent to {{para|talk}}){{colon}}
: {{tnull|Update|'''talk{{=}}Shall we update this for {{CURRENTYEAR}}?'''|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
;To display a reason (after the added phrase "In particular{{colon}}"), use {{para|reason|{{var|a short comment here}}}}, e.g.{{colon}}
: {{tnull|Update|'''reason{{=}}Is missing the {{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}} election results'''|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
; These parameters can be combined, of course{{colon}}:
: {{tnull|Update |part{{=}}The <nowiki>[[#Production|Production]]</nowiki> section and follow-on material&nbsp;|reason{{=}}the film is released, so this needs a "Critical reception" section, too&nbsp;|inaccurate{{=}}yes&nbsp;|talk{{=}}Post-release updating&nbsp;|updated{{=}}{{#time:F Y|-3 month}}&nbsp;|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}

===Example===
{{tlx|Update|documentation|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
{{Update|documentation}}

