* To display a reason, use {{para|reason|{{var|a short comment here}}}}, e.g. {{tnull|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|reason{{=}}The service offerings should reflect new repair technologies and products|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
* These parameters can be combined: {{tnull|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|part{{=}}The repair services and models need an update for the latest offerings|reason{{=}}new models added to the repair catalog|inaccurate{{=}}yes|talk{{=}}Post-service update|updated{{=}}{{#time:F Y|-3 month}}|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}

